caption:
Spring has sprung with this adorable treat 🌼

Ingredients:
1 Box JELL-O Chocolate Pudding
Chocolate Cookies
Jet-Puffed Marshmallows
Chocolate Candies

How to Make It:
1. Prepare JELL-O according to the instructions on package. Crush chocolate cookies.
2. In a cup, layer JELL-O pudding and crushed cookies.
3. Cut a Jet-Puffed Marshmallow into thin pieces. Arrange in the shape of a flower, with the chocolate candy as the center. Place atop your JELL-O pudding cup and enjoy!
